            <div type="transcript" id="F595A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Lightning playeth - all<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the while -</l>
                    <l>But when He singeth - then - </l>
                    <l>Ourselves are conscious He exist - </l>
                    <l>And we approach Him - stern - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>With Insulators - and a Glove -</l>
                    <l>Whose short - sepulchral Bass </l>
                    <l>Alarms us - tho' His Yellow feet </l>
                    <l>May pass - and counterpass - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Opon the Ropes - above our Head - </l>
                    <l>Continual - with the News -</l>
                    <l>Nor We so much as check<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 our speech - </l>
                    <l>Nor stop to cross Ourselves - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
